Module com.example.platformerplain
Package com.example.platformerplain.util

Class GameInitializer

java.lang.Object
com.example.platformerplain.util.GameInitializer
public class GameInitializer extends Object
Provides utility methods to initialize and start the game.

The GameInitializer class contains static methods to set up and initialise the game environment, including creating the game view, player, game controller, and scene.

It also manages loading level data and configuring the primary stage.
